data.description: $34K PRICE DROP (incl. $5K credit on FPO)! Looking for peace & quiet with potential to add sweat equity value? This may be it! One & 1/2 story, 1,438 finished S.F., 3-bed, 1 bath home on private well & septic (means no utility co. fees) on over an acre, mostly level, lot. Additional unfinished 504 s.f. in basement for higher value, +-1,950 s.f. home when finished. Older home w/ good bones ready for new owner looking to create equity w/ cosmetic updates & TLC. New carpet & paint will make a huge difference. Interested in going off-grid? Add solar panels, chicken coop & veggie patch.. the back yard is ideal! A few minutes to County Park & Chehalis River. 20 mins to State Park (Lake Sylvia). +-30 mins to DT Olympia & an hour from Ocean Shores.
